sdl_gfx: SDL_gfx (SDL_graphic components)
sdl_gfx:
sdl_gfx: The SDL_gfx library offers several components: Graphic Primitives,
sdl_gfx: Rotozoomer, Framerate control, and MMX image filters. The Primitives
sdl_gfx: component provides basic drawing routines: pixels, hlines, vlines,
sdl_gfx: lines, aa-lines, rectangles, circles, ellipses, trigons, polygons,
sdl_gfx: Bezier curves, and an 8x8 pixmap font for drawing onto any SDL
sdl_gfx: Surface. Full alpha blending, hardware surface locking, and all
sdl_gfx: surface depths are supported.
sdl_gfx: http://www.ferzkopp.net/~aschiffler/Software/SDL_gfx-2.0/
sdl_gfx: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
